column5: Well Corey (mistyjr) has compiled some of our highlights of our 2006 fishing season.  Included are two trips to Lakair, our trip to Tennessee, a couple of my outings with some pretty well known OFNr's , ice fishing and several day/weekend trips.     We've added some audio with Green Day's "Time of your Life".  I think it is a pretty appropriate song if you listen to the lyrics.    Some of the pictures are a little blurry, but you'll get the jist of it.   Great job Corey   , I hope everyone enjoys....  http://video.google.ca/videoplay?docid=4541097321236595496
What an awesome job! I laughed, I cried!  I hope 2007 is just as successful!
Beautiful job on the video Cory, and it looks like you and your family had a summer you'll remember for a looooong time
Great review, song fits!  Great job.  Whopper

Awesome Job Corey.  You guys had a fabulous season and one I'm sure you will remember for the  rest of your life.  Dad is setting a great example for you when you have kids. Only one complaint.  I could have sworn thare was one monster fish missing. Would have been a good time to bring it out of the closet Time of your life is a favourite of the FishGuts I'll have to go back and watch it again! You put a lot of time into that!

I CANT COMPLIMENT YOU ENOUGH AFTER SEEING ALL THOSE PICS WITH KIDS IN THEM!! KIDS ARE THE FUTURE OF THIS FISHERY!!! GREAT TO SEE AT YOUNG AGES THEM ENJOYING THEMSELVES!! GETS BORING SEE PICS OF ADULTS AND FISH AGAIN AND AGAIN( INCLUDING MESELF  LOL) BUT YA CAN NEVER GET BORED OF SEEING THE KIDS!! ITS A SMILE AND ENJOYMENT WE JUST CANT COPY ANYMORE AS ADULTS!! WELL DONE GUYZ!!
well done
As one of the FishGuts gang, I have to agree with BPSBASSMAN. Great Slideshow to go with a Great Song. Nicely done.
Excellent job Corey.  I hope 2007 brings more fishing enjoyment  to you and your family. (if it's possible to top the great 2006 you had?)
Wow, I love it!!!  Great job Corey, very nice work bud!!!
Nice job.  I love that song too!  Nice little reminder of good times to view in the future.  Good idea.  Joey
WOW!!!  That was a lot of effort I bet, but well worth it! Well done Corey! You guys have had a phenomenal year!
awsome!!  Really enjoyed that  - job very well done! Thank You for posting it.    Don
well that was,very cool,what a way to sum up your fishing year,well done   and all those fish pictures says it all
Very well done guys, what a great season you had!  Roger, I think I saw it, watch it again....  I think I also recognized a couple of guys too!
Excellent!!!
....Lovely, just lovely.
Nice job, mistyjr!    Mike
Thanks for sharing. I enjoyed that.
Very well done, I do remember most of those pictures.
